thread.title_full: MicksGarage.com reviewed by Keith, Leopardstown, Dublin

author: Keith, Leopardstown, Dublin
title: Keith, Leopardstown, Dublin
text: I ordered new wipers for my Santa Fe 131. The process was easy and collection was local to where I work. The whole process was a doddle BUT the wipers they fitted fine except for the dimension difference to the original. I selected the exact make and model (not using the registration) and everything was matched. Now I have to live with that horrible triangle that is not wiped as the new wipers are 2 inches smaller than the original!! Frustration
